line_1: Than each of them could carry on their Backs.
line_2: Out of the City, with no bigger Packs

line_1: It ought to bring all Courtiers on their backs.
line_2: Now pox on those who shew a Court in Wax!

line_1: But Merran sat behint their backs,
line_2: She lea'es them gashan at their cracks,

line_1: All the while an old Woman was rubbing their Backs!
line_2: How the Ladies did giggle and set up their Clacks,
